#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:1
msgid "Multi-Model Setup and Fallback Chains"
msgstr "マルチモデル設定とフォールバックチェーン"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:3
msgid ""
"This guide introduces multi-model concepts in ZeroClaw, including fallback "
"provider chains, model-level fallbacks, and API key rotation for resilience."
msgstr ""
"このガイドでは、ZeroClawのマルチモデルコンセプト（フォールバックプロバイダー"
"チェーン、モデルレベルのフォールバック、耐障害性のためのAPIキーローテーショ"
"ン）を紹介します。"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:5
msgid "When to Use Multi-Model Setup"
msgstr "マルチモデル設定を使用する場合"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:7
msgid "Multi-model configuration is useful for:"
msgstr "マルチモデル設定は以下の場合に役立ちます："

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:9
msgid ""
"**High reliability**: Automatically fall back to alternative providers when "
"the primary fails"
msgstr ""
"**高い信頼性**: プライマリプロバイダーが失敗した場合、自動的に代替プロバイ"
"ダーにフォールバック"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:10
msgid ""
"**Cost optimization**: Route expensive models through fallback chains for "
"rate-limited scenarios"
msgstr ""
"**コスト最適化**: レート制限シナリオで高コストモデルをフォールバックチェーン"
"経由でルーティング"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:11
msgid ""
"**Regional resilience**: Use geographically distributed providers to handle "
"region-specific outages"
msgstr ""
"**地域的耐障害性**: 地理的に分散したプロバイダーを使用して地域固有の障害に対"
"応"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:12
msgid ""
"**Capability flexibility**: Try different models when one lacks required "
"features (e.g., tool calling, vision)"
msgstr ""
"**機能の柔軟性**: 必要な機能がないモデル（ツール呼び出しやビジョンなど）があ"
"る場合、異なるモデルを試す"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:13
msgid ""
"**Rate limit handling**: Rotate through API keys on `429` (rate limit) "
"responses"
msgstr ""
"**レート制限処理**: `429`（レート制限）レスポンスでAPIキーをローテーション"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:14
msgid ""
"**Development and testing**: Switch between cloud and local models without "
"code changes"
msgstr ""
"**開発とテスト**: コードを変更せずにクラウドモデルとローカルモデルを切り替え"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:16
msgid "Core Concepts"
msgstr "コアコンセプト"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:18
msgid "Fallback Provider Chains"
msgstr "フォールバックプロバイダーチェーン"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:20
msgid ""
"When a provider experiences a transient error (timeout, connection failure, "
"auth issue), ZeroClaw automatically attempts fallback providers in the order "
"specified."
msgstr ""
"プロバイダーが一時的なエラー（タイムアウト、接続失敗、認証エラー）に遭遇する"
"と、ZeroClawは指定された順序でフォールバックプロバイダーを自動的に試みます。"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:22
msgid ""
"**Example**: If your primary provider is `openai` but it's temporarily "
"unavailable, ZeroClaw can automatically fall back to `anthropic`, then "
"`groq`."
msgstr ""
"**例**: プライマリプロバイダーが `openai` だが一時的に利用不可の場合、"
"ZeroClawは自動的に `anthropic` にフォールバックし、次に `groq` を試します。"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:24
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"fallback_providers = [\"anthropic\", \"groq\", \"openrouter\"]\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```toml\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"fallback_providers = [\"anthropic\", \"groq\", \"openrouter\"]\n"
"```"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:29
msgid ""
"When the primary provider recovers, ZeroClaw resumes using it (no sticky "
"failover)."
msgstr ""
"プライマリプロバイダーが復旧すると、ZeroClawはそれを使用再開します（スティッ"
"キーフェイルオーバーなし）。"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:31
msgid "Model-Level Fallbacks"
msgstr "モデルレベルのフォールバック"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:33
msgid ""
"Some models may not be available in all regions, or you might want to use a "
"faster model when a heavy model is rate-limited."
msgstr ""
"一部のモデルはすべてのリージョンで利用できない場合があります。または、重いモ"
"デルがレート制限されている場合により高速なモデルを使用したい場合があります。"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:35
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"model_fallbacks = { \"claude-opus-4-7\" = [\"claude-sonnet-4-6\", "
"\"gpt-4o\"] }\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```toml\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"model_fallbacks = { \"claude-opus-4-7\" = [\"claude-sonnet-4-6\", "
"\"gpt-4o\"] }\n"
"```"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:40
msgid ""
"If `claude-opus-4-7` fails or is unavailable, ZeroClaw tries the fallback "
"models in order while staying within the same provider (unless a provider-"
"level fallback is also configured)."
msgstr ""
"`claude-opus-4-7` が失敗または利用不可の場合、ZeroClawはプロバイダーレベルの"
"フォールバックも設定されていない限り、同じプロバイダー内でフォールバックモデ"
"ルを順番に試します。"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:42
msgid "API Key Rotation"
msgstr "APIキーローテーション"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:44
msgid ""
"For providers that frequently encounter rate limits, you can supply "
"additional API keys that ZeroClaw will rotate through on `429` responses."
msgstr ""
"頻繁にレート制限に遭遇するプロバイダーの場合、ZeroClawが `429` レスポンスで"
"ローテーションするための追加APIキーを指定できます。"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:46
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"api_keys = [\"sk-key-2\", \"sk-key-3\", \"sk-key-4\"]\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```toml\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"api_keys = [\"sk-key-2\", \"sk-key-3\", \"sk-key-4\"]\n"
"```"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:51
msgid ""
"The primary `api_key` (configured globally or per-channel) is always tried "
"first; these extras are rotated on rate-limit errors."
msgstr ""
"プライマリ `api_key`（グローバルまたはチャネルごとに設定）は常に最初に試さ"
"れ、これらの追加キーはレート制限エラーでローテーションされます。"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:53
msgid "Provider Retries"
msgstr "プロバイダー再試行"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:55
msgid ""
"Each provider attempt includes configurable retries with exponential backoff "
"before moving to the next fallback."
msgstr ""
"各プロバイダーの試行は、次のフォールバックに移動する前に、指数バックオフを使"
"用した再試行可能な再試行を含みます。"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:63
msgid "Configuration Structure"
msgstr "設定構造"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:65
msgid ""
"All multi-model behavior lives under the `[reliability]` section of "
"`config.toml`. See the [Config reference](../reference/config.md) for the "
"full field index and defaults."
msgstr ""
"すべてのマルチモデル動作は `config.toml` の `[reliability]` セクションに配置"
"されます。全フィールドインデックスとデフォルトについては[Config リファレンス]"
"(../reference/config.md)を参照してください。"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:67
msgid "Example Configurations"
msgstr "設定例"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:69
msgid "Basic Fallback Chain"
msgstr "基本的なフォールバックチェーン"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:71
msgid "Set up a simple fallback from your primary provider to a backup:"
msgstr ""
"プライマリプロバイダーからバックアップへの単純なフォールバックを設定します："

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:73
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"default_provider = \"openai\"\n"
"default_model = \"gpt-4o\"\n"
"\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"fallback_providers = [\"anthropic\"]\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```toml\n"
"default_provider = \"openai\"\n"
"default_model = \"gpt-4o\"\n"
"\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"fallback_providers = [\"anthropic\"]\n"
"```"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:81
msgid ""
"**Behavior**: If OpenAI times out or returns an error, ZeroClaw will retry "
"twice with exponential backoff, then attempt the same request using "
"Anthropic."
msgstr ""

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:83
msgid "High-Reliability Multi-Provider Setup"
msgstr "高信頼性マルチプロバイダー設定"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:85
msgid "Combine provider fallbacks with model fallbacks and API key rotation:"
msgstr ""
"プロバイダーフォールバックをモデルフォールバックおよびAPIキーローテーションと"
"組み合わせます："

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:87
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"default_provider = \"openai\"\n"
"default_model = \"gpt-4o\"\n"
"api_key = \"sk-openai-primary\"\n"
"\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"fallback_providers = [\"anthropic\", \"groq\", \"openrouter\"]\n"
"api_keys = [\"sk-openai-backup-1\", \"sk-openai-backup-2\"]\n"
"\n"
"[reliability.model_fallbacks]\n"
"\"gpt-4o\" = [\"gpt-4-turbo\", \"gpt-3.5-turbo\"]\n"
"\"gpt-4-turbo\" = [\"gpt-3.5-turbo\"]\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```toml\n"
"default_provider = \"openai\"\n"
"default_model = \"gpt-4o\"\n"
"api_key = \"sk-openai-primary\"\n"
"\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"fallback_providers = [\"anthropic\", \"groq\", \"openrouter\"]\n"
"api_keys = [\"sk-openai-backup-1\", \"sk-openai-backup-2\"]\n"
"\n"
"[reliability.model_fallbacks]\n"
"\"gpt-4o\" = [\"gpt-4-turbo\", \"gpt-3.5-turbo\"]\n"
"\"gpt-4-turbo\" = [\"gpt-3.5-turbo\"]\n"
"```"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:101
msgid "**Behavior**:"
msgstr "**動作**："

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:102
msgid "Try OpenAI `gpt-4o` with primary key (2 retries)"
msgstr "プライマリキーで OpenAI `gpt-4o` を試行（2回の再試行）"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:103
msgid "On rate-limit, rotate to backup API keys"
msgstr "レート制限時にバックアップAPIキーにローテーション"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:104
msgid ""
"If OpenAI still fails, fall back to Anthropic with same model request "
"(Anthropic will select available equivalent)"
msgstr ""
"OpenAIが依然として失敗した場合、同じモデルリクエストでAnthropicにフォールバッ"
"ク（Anthropicが利用可能な同等のものを選択）"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:105
msgid "If Anthropic unavailable, try Groq, then OpenRouter"
msgstr "Anthropropicが利用不可の場合、Groq、次にOpenRouterを試す"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:106
msgid "If model not available, try fallback models in order"
msgstr "モデルが利用不可の場合、フォールバックモデルを順番に試す"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:108
msgid "Local Development with Cloud Fallback"
msgstr "クラウドフォールバック付きローカル開発"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:110
msgid "Use a local Ollama instance as primary, fall back to cloud provider:"
msgstr ""
"ローカルOllamaインスタンスをプライマリとして使用し、クラウドプロバイダーに"
"フォールバック："

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:112
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"default_provider = \"ollama\"\n"
"default_model = \"llama2:70b\"\n"
"api_url = \"http://localhost:11434\"\n"
"\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"fallback_providers = [\"openrouter\", \"groq\"]\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```toml\n"
"default_provider = \"ollama\"\n"
"default_model = \"llama2:70b\"\n"
"api_url = \"http://localhost:11434\"\n"
"\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"fallback_providers = [\"openrouter\", \"groq\"]\n"
"```"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:121
msgid ""
"**Behavior**: If Ollama goes down or times out, automatically use OpenRouter "
"or Groq instead without configuration changes."
msgstr ""
"**動作**: Ollamaがダウンするか、タイムアウトする場合、設定の変更なしに自動的"
"にOpenRouterまたはGroqを使用します。"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:123
msgid "Cost Optimization: Heavy Model with Fast Fallback"
msgstr "コスト最適化：高コストモデルと高速フォールバック"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:125
msgid ""
"Use an expensive reasoning model for complex tasks, but fall back to a "
"faster model:"
msgstr ""
"複雑なタスク用に高コストの推論モデルを使用しますが、より高速なモデルにフォー"
"ルバック："

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:127
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"default_provider = \"anthropic\"\n"
"default_model = \"claude-opus-4-7\"\n"
"\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"model_fallbacks = { \"claude-opus-4-7\" = [\"claude-sonnet-4-6\"] }\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```toml\n"
"default_provider = \"anthropic\"\n"
"default_model = \"claude-opus-4-7\"\n"
"\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"model_fallbacks = { \"claude-opus-4-7\" = [\"claude-sonnet-4-6\"] }\n"
"```"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:135
msgid ""
"**Behavior**: When Opus is rate-limited or slow, automatically use Sonnet "
"(typically 2–3x faster and cheaper)."
msgstr ""
"**動作**: Opusがレート制限されるか遅い場合、自動的にSonnet（通常2～3倍高速か"
"つ安い）を使用します。"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:137
msgid "Multi-Region Setup"
msgstr "マルチリージョンセットアップ"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:139
msgid "For organizations with multi-region deployments:"
msgstr "マルチリージョンデプロイメントを行う組織の場合:"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:141
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"# Primary US region\n"
"default_provider = \"anthropic\"\n"
"default_model = \"claude-sonnet-4-6\"\n"
"\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"# Fall back to EU region provider if US Anthropic is down\n"
"fallback_providers = [\"bedrock\"]  # AWS Bedrock in multiple regions\n"
"provider_retries = 3\n"
"provider_backoff_ms = 1000\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```toml\n"
"# Primary US region\n"
"default_provider = \"anthropic\"\n"
"default_model = \"claude-sonnet-4-6\"\n"
"\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"# Fall back to EU region provider if US Anthropic is down\n"
"fallback_providers = [\"bedrock\"]  # AWS Bedrock in multiple regions\n"
"provider_retries = 3\n"
"provider_backoff_ms = 1000\n"
"```"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:153
msgid "Ensure each fallback provider has credentials in your environment:"
msgstr ""
"各フォールバックプロバイダーが環境に認証情報を持っていることを確認してくださ"
"い:"

