msgid "Translate the app strings:"
msgstr ""

#: src/maintainers/docs-and-translations.md:183
msgid "Bootstrap and fill the docs `.po` file:"
msgstr ""

#: src/maintainers/docs-and-translations.md:188
msgid ""
"Everything else — `lang-switcher.js`, CI deploy — reads from `locales.toml` "
"automatically."
msgstr ""

#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md:3
msgid "Automatic workflows"
msgstr ""

#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md:5
msgid "Quality Gate (`ci.yml`)"
msgstr ""

#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md:7
msgid "Fires on every PR targeting `master`. Two sequential stages:"
msgstr ""

#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md:9
msgid ""
"**Lint** — `cargo fmt --check` + `cargo clippy --features ci-all -D "
"warnings`. Fails fast before burning compute on the build stage."
msgstr ""

#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md:10
msgid "**Build** — cross-platform matrix build. Runs only if lint passes."
msgstr ""

#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md:12
msgid "A PR cannot merge until this workflow is green."
msgstr ""

#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md:14
msgid "Deploy Docs (`docs-deploy.yml`)"
msgstr ""

#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md:16
msgid ""
"Fires automatically on push to `master` (and `feat/fluent-i18n` during "
"development) when any of the following change: `docs/book/**`, `src/**`, "
"`crates/**`, `Cargo.toml`, `Cargo.lock`."
msgstr ""

#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md:20
msgid ""
"Generates `docs/book/src/reference/cli.md` and `config.md` from the live code"
msgstr ""

#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md:21
msgid "Generates the rustdoc API reference"
msgstr ""

#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md:22
msgid ""
"Validates `.po` format — **fails the deploy if any `.po` file is malformed**"
msgstr ""

#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md:23
msgid ""
"Builds mdBook for every locale in `locales.toml` → `docs/book/book/{locale}/`"
msgstr ""

#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md:24
msgid "Assembles the Pages artifact (rustdoc + locale redirect `index.html`)"
msgstr ""

#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md:25
msgid "Deploys to GitHub Pages"
msgstr ""

#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md:27
msgid ""
"**If it fails:** most common causes are a malformed `.po` file (run `cargo "
"mdbook check` locally) or a broken reference page (run `cargo mdbook refs` "
"and check for panics in `markdown-help` or `markdown-schema`)."
msgstr ""

#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md:29
msgid "Daily Audit (`daily-audit.yml`)"
msgstr ""

#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md:31
msgid ""
"Runs `cargo audit` nightly against the dependency tree. Opens an issue on "
"findings."
msgstr ""

#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md:33
msgid "PR Path Labeler (`pr-path-labeler.yml`)"
msgstr ""

#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md:35
msgid ""
"Auto-applies scope and risk labels based on changed file paths. No action "
"needed — runs silently on every PR."
msgstr ""

#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md:37
msgid "Manual workflows"
msgstr ""

#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md:39
msgid "Translate Docs (`docs-translate.yml`)"
msgstr ""

#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md:41
msgid ""
"Run this before a release to AI-fill any untranslated or fuzzy strings in "
"the `.po` files. It commits updated `.po` files back to the current branch, "
"which then triggers `docs-deploy.yml`."
msgstr ""

#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md:43
msgid "**Trigger:** Actions → _Translate docs (manual)_ → Run workflow"
msgstr ""

