"ttyACM0 zeroclaw hardware info --chip STM32F401RETx"
msgstr ""
"例: zeroclaw hardware discover zeroclaw hardware introspect /dev/ttyACM0 "
"zeroclaw hardware info --chip STM32F401RETx"

