"expression = \"0 9 * * *\"\n"
"```"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:1
msgid "SOP Syntax Reference"
msgstr "SOP 構文リファレンス"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:3
msgid ""
"SOP definitions are loaded from subdirectories under `sops_dir` (default: "
"`<workspace>/sops`)."
msgstr ""
"SOP 定義は`sops_dir`(デフォルト: `<workspace>/sops`)の下のサブディレクトリか"
"ら読み込まれます。"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:5
msgid "1. Directory Layout"
msgstr "1. ディレクトリレイアウト"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:14
msgid ""
"Each SOP must have `SOP.toml`. `SOP.md` is optional, but runs with no parsed "
"steps will fail validation."
msgstr ""
"各 SOP には`SOP.toml`が必要です。`SOP.md`はオプションですが、パースされたス"
"テップがない場合は検証に失敗します。"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:16
msgid "2. `SOP.toml`"
msgstr "2. `SOP.toml`"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:18
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[sop]\n"
"name = \"deploy-prod\"\n"
"description = \"Deploy service to production\"\n"
"version = \"1.0.0\"\n"
"priority = \"high\"              # low | normal | high | critical\n"
"execution_mode = \"supervised\"  # auto | supervised | step_by_step | "
"priority_based\n"
"cooldown_secs = 300\n"
"max_concurrent = 1\n"
"\n"
"[[triggers]]\n"
"type = \"webhook\"\n"
"path = \"/sop/deploy\"\n"
"\n"
"[[triggers]]\n"
"type = \"manual\"\n"
"\n"
"[[triggers]]\n"
"type = \"mqtt\"\n"
"topic = \"ops/deploy\"\n"
"condition = \"$.env == \\\"prod\\\"\"\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```toml\n"
"[sop]\n"
"name = \"deploy-prod\"\n"
"description = \"Deploy service to production\"\n"
"version = \"1.0.0\"\n"
"priority = \"high\"              # low | normal | high | critical\n"
"execution_mode = \"supervised\"  # auto | supervised | step_by_step | "
"priority_based\n"
"cooldown_secs = 300\n"
"max_concurrent = 1\n"
"\n"
"[[triggers]]\n"
"type = \"webhook\"\n"
"path = \"/sop/deploy\"\n"
"\n"
"[[triggers]]\n"
"type = \"manual\"\n"
"\n"
"[[triggers]]\n"
"type = \"mqtt\"\n"
"topic = \"ops/deploy\"\n"
"condition = \"$.env == \\\"prod\\\"\"\n"
"```"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:41
msgid "3. `SOP.md` Step Format"
msgstr "3. `SOP.md` ステップ形式"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:43
msgid "Steps are parsed from the `## Steps` section."
msgstr "ステップは`## Steps`セクションからパースされます。"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:56
msgid "Parser behavior:"
msgstr "パーサーの動作:"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:58
msgid "Numbered items (`1.`, `2.`, ...) define step order."
msgstr "番号付きアイテム(`1.`、`2.`、...)はステップの順序を定義します。"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:59
msgid "Leading bold text (`**Title**`) becomes step title."
msgstr "先頭の太字テキスト(`**Title**`)はステップのタイトルになります。"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:60
msgid "`- tools:` maps to `suggested_tools`."
msgstr "`- tools:`は`suggested_tools`にマップされます。"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:61
msgid "`- requires_confirmation: true` enforces approval for that step."
msgstr ""
"`- requires_confirmation: true`は、そのステップに対して承認を強制します。"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:63
msgid "4. Trigger Types"
msgstr "4. トリガータイプ"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:65
msgid "Fields"
msgstr "フィールド"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:67
msgid "`manual`"
msgstr "`manual`"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:67
msgid "none"
msgstr ""
"`sop_execute`ツールによってトリガーされます(`zeroclaw sop run` CLI コマンドで"
"はありません)。"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:67
msgid "Triggered by tool `sop_execute` (not a `zeroclaw sop run` CLI command)."
msgstr "リクエストパスに対する完全一致(`/sop/...`または`/webhook`)。"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:68
msgid "`path`"
msgstr "`topic`、オプションの`condition`"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:68
msgid "Exact match against request path (`/sop/...` or `/webhook`)."
msgstr "MQTT トピックは`+`と`#`ワイルドカードをサポートしています。"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:69
msgid "`topic`, optional `condition`"
msgstr "`expression`"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:69
msgid "MQTT topic supports `+` and `#` wildcards."
msgstr ""
"5、6、または 7 フィールドをサポートしています(5 フィールドは内部的に秒が前置"
"されます)。"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:70
msgid "`expression`"
msgstr "`peripheral`"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:70
msgid "Supports 5, 6, or 7 fields (5-field gets seconds prepended internally)."
msgstr "`board`、`signal`、オプションの`condition`"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:71
msgid "`peripheral`"
msgstr "`\"{board}/{signal}\"`にマッチします。"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:71
msgid "`board`, `signal`, optional `condition`"
msgstr "5. 条件構文"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:71
msgid "Matches `\"{board}/{signal}\"`."
msgstr ""
"`condition`はフェイルクローズドで評価されます(無効な条件/ペイロード => マッチ"
"なし)。"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:73
msgid "5. Condition Syntax"
msgstr "JSON パス比較: `$.value > 85`、`$.status == \"critical\"`"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:75
msgid ""
"`condition` is evaluated fail-closed (invalid condition/payload => no match)."
msgstr "直接数値比較: `> 0`(シンプルペイロード用)"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:77
msgid "JSON path comparisons: `$.value > 85`, `$.status == \"critical\"`"
msgstr "演算子: `>=`、`<=`、`!=`、`>`、`<`、`==`"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:78
msgid "Direct numeric comparisons: `> 0` (useful for simple payloads)"
msgstr "6. 検証"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:79
msgid "Operators: `>=`, `<=`, `!=`, `>`, `<`, `==`"
msgstr "使用:"

#: src/reference/sop/syntax.md:81
msgid "6. Validation"
msgstr ""
"検証は空の名前/説明、トリガー欠落、ステップ欠落、ステップ番号の間隔に対して警"
