"type = \"mqtt\"\n"
"topic = \"sensors/alert\"\n"
"condition = \"$.severity >= 2\"\n"
"```"

#: src/reference/sop/connectivity.md:40
msgid ""
"MQTT payload is forwarded into SOP event payload (`event.payload`), then "
